### 4. Location Update (REST)
```
POST /location/update
```
```json
{
  "id": 1,
  "role": "driver",
  "lat": 12.9750,
  "lng": 77.5900
}
```
- **Driver**: Saves to DB + broadcasts `DRIVER_LOCATION` to the user who has an active ride with this driver
- **User**: Acknowledges receipt (pickup location is already stored when ride is created)

